OL,6,FA woman sacked by her chef husband
OL,7,Fafter she caught him having an affair
OL,8,Fwith his sous chef has been awarded
OL,9,Fnearly #10,000 in compensation.
OL,11,FJacqueline Herling confronted Stefan
OL,12,FHerling in May 2022, telling him she
OL,13,Fhad seen CCTV footage of his
OL,14,Finfidelity at the Beehive Inn, their
OL,15,Fbusiness in Combs, Derbyshire.
OL,17,FDuring a heated row, Mrs Herling said
OL,18,Fshe "would not set foot in the pub
OL,19,Fagain", an employment tribunal was
OL,20,Ftold.
