OL,6,FMrs Herling, who began working at the
OL,7,Fpub in 2003, sued her husband and the
OL,8,Ffamily business for unfair and
OL,9,Fwrongful dismissal, unauthorised pay
OL,10,Fdeductions and victimisation, after he
OL,11,Fissued her with a P45.
OL,13,FThe couple, who married in 2008, have
OL,14,Ftwo children together, and were all
OL,15,Fliving together in the pub, a
OL,16,FManchester employment tribunal heard.
