OL,4,Cwins payout
OL,6,FAfter the argument, Mrs Herling never
OL,7,Fmoved out, but reduced her work to
OL,8,F"occasional duties" such as chopping
OL,9,Flogs and mowing the lawns, the
OL,10,Ftribunal was told.
OL,12,FMr Herling told his wife to "think
OL,13,Fabout things and take her time before
OL,14,Fmaking any or any long-term
OL,15,Fdecisions", but she began divorce
OL,16,Fproceedings in July 2022, the tribunal
OL,17,Fheard.
